    <h2>Benefits</h2>

    <h3>Collaboration</h3>

    <p>
      Seshy handles all the messy details about transporting complex DAW sessions from one computer to another.
    </p>
    <p>
      Teams make it effortless for you to work with repeat collaborators and it's easy to invite new ones.
    </p>

    <h3>Backup</h3>

    <p>Every change you make to a session is automatically backed up to the cloud as long as you have Seshy running.</p>

    <h3>Archiving</h3>

    <p>Store every version of your projects, so that if you decide that you've taken a wrong turn, it's easy to go back to a previous version.</p>
