    <h2>What do subscriptions include?</h2>

    <p>Each plan comes with a <b>Storage Pool</b> and some number of <b>Umbrella Subscriptions</b></p>
    <ul>
      <li>The <b>Storage Pool</b> is the maximum amount of project data that your team can own.</li>
      <li><b>Umbrella Subsacriptions</b> allow you to extend your <b>Storage Pool</b> to cover projects owned by additional teams.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>All paid plans allow for <b>Unlimited Projects</b>, <b>Unlimited Teams</b>, and <b>Unlimited Collaborators</b>.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="/subscriptions/">Learn more about how subscriptions work.</a>
    </p>
  </div>

